Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.22,0:01:11.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}果酱伙伴! \N{\rENG}Jam buds!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}表演的不错\N{\rENG}Nice jam session.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.40,0:01:14.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别忘的最好的部分\N{\rENG}Don't forget the best part.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}逃向你们的主人吧! \N{\rENG}Run back to your masters!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}告诉他们 我们无所畏惧! \N{\rENG}Tell them we're not afraid of your kind!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你拯救了我的果酱小食\N{\rENG}Thanks for saving my jam snack.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不幸的是 它还是会因我遭殃\N{\rENG}Unfortunately, it's not safe from me.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真是个优秀的剑士啊 康妮\N{\rENG}You're such a good sword fighter, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的? 我刚才只是在随便挥舞这个而已\N{\rENG}Really? I was just swinging this thing around.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我并不清楚自己在做什么\N{\rENG}I don't really know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.86,0:01:45.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我非常想学习如何使用真剑\N{\rENG}But I'd love to learn how to use a real sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 史蒂文有个主意! \N{\rENG}Oh! Steven has an idea!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想让我做什么? \N{\rENG}You want me to do what?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一定要教康妮剑术\N{\rENG}You should train Connie to sword fight.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她现在已经非常出色了\N{\rENG}She's already so good.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 你帮我打败了飞行机器人\N{\rENG}But you are. Y-you helped me fight the robot floaty thing,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她打败了自己的邪恶克隆体\N{\rENG}she took down that evil clone of herself,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...还有刚才的那些坏海鸥\N{\rENG}uh...Those mean seagulls just now.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你现在接触这种东西还是太小了\N{\rENG}You're awfully young to begin something like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我想我开始与玫瑰·石英一起战斗时\N{\rENG}But I suppose I was only a few thousand years old
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也才几千岁而已\N{\rENG}when I begin fighting alongside Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么 康妮? \N{\rENG}Yes, Connie?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}求求你 我想学\N{\rENG}Please, I want to learn.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是指 我不知道以后会发生什么\N{\rENG}I mean, I don't know what will happen in the future.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但如果出现了危险的情况\N{\rENG}But if something dangerous comes along,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不想成为负担 我想要帮忙! \N{\rENG}I don't want to be a burden. I want to help!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想帮助史蒂文 与他肩并肩战斗! \N{\rENG}I want to be there for Steven, to fight by his side!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.61,0:02:29.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球也是我的家 我就不能帮忙保护吗? \N{\rENG}The earth is my home, too. Can't I help protect it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}O-okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你是这么认为的 那我们该开始了\N{\rENG}If that's how you feel, we should get started.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 现在? \N{\rENG}Wait, now?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还好吗? \N{\rENG}You okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可能要花些功夫适应\N{\rENG}It can take some getting used to.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你们两个 这里\N{\rENG}Hey, you two. This way.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}比比看\N{\rENG}Race you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是个远古天空角斗场 康妮\N{\rENG}This is an ancient sky arena, Connie,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.01,0:03:01.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球独立战争早期的部分战役也是在这里发生的\N{\rENG}where some of the first battles for earth took place.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就是在这里了解了\N{\rENG}It was here that I became familiar with
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类对于骑士的概念\N{\rENG}the human concept of being a knight,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.86,0:03:08.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}完全献身于某个人或理念\N{\rENG}completely dedicated to a person and a cause.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你必须要成为这样的人 康妮--\N{\rENG}This is what you must become, Connie--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}勇敢 无私 忠诚--骑士\N{\rENG}brave, selfless, loyal--a knight.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.06,0:03:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们先从躬身开始 首先对我 你的老师\N{\rENG}We begin with a bow. First to me, your teacher.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后是你的君主\N{\rENG}And now again to your liege.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的 我的君主\N{\rENG}Okay. My liege.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}骑士小姐\N{\rENG}Miss knight.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.48,0:03:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望你们两个能严肃点\N{\rENG}I hope you two are taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的 夫人\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}酷 全息珍珠\N{\rENG}Cool. Hologram Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}首先 这个全息珍珠是你的对手\N{\rENG}To begin, this holo-Pearl will be your opponent.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}第0级 初学者设置\N{\rENG}Level 0, beginner set.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是否愿意进入战斗? \N{\rENG}Do you wish to engage in combat?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然! \N{\rENG}Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.19,0:03:48.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文? \N{\rENG}Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 呃 我很抱歉\N{\rENG}Oh! Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}抱歉 抱歉 抱歉 抱歉\N{\rENG}Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}条件反射\N{\rENG}Reflex.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 你小心点 我会去那里待着\N{\rENG}Uh, you just be careful, and I will go over here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.50,0:04:02.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 一切先从你的站姿开始\N{\rENG}All right. Everything begins with your stance.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}要记住...你为他而战\N{\rENG}Remember...♪ you do it for him
Dialogue: 150,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.30,Song Lyrics Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}而你愿再次出征\N{\rENG_LYC}♪ and you would do it again ♪
