Dialogue: 600,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.04,Hint,,0,0,0,,史蒂文手中的书源自卡耐基的名书 "人性的弱点"( How to Win Friends and Influence People)
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Hey, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 等等\N{\rENG}Connie, wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊 真准时\N{\rENG}Ah, right on time.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.74,0:06:25.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能先谈一下吗? \N{\rENG}Can we talk for a moment?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 怎么了? \N{\rENG}Sure. What's up?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们还有重要的训练要完成 康妮\N{\rENG}We have important training to do, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的 女士\N{\rENG}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她最近进步非常大 史蒂文\N{\rENG}She's been making great strides, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她会成为你的得力部下\N{\rENG}She's going to be an asset to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.68,0:06:40.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 石榴\N{\rENG}Wow, Garnet.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是我听过的最有趣的故事\N{\rENG}That was the funniest thing I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴 喜剧之王\N{\rENG}Garnet, master of comedy.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.72,0:06:46.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呦 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Yo, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么一脸苦逼的站在那?!\N{\rENG}Why are you standing there all sad like that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 康妮正跟着珍珠学习剑术\N{\rENG}W-well, Connie is taking sword-fighting lessons from Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我觉得训练有点太过了\N{\rENG}But I think it's getting a little too serious.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她想让康妮替我完成所有危险的事\N{\rENG}She wants Connie to do all this dangerous stuff for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这很正常\N{\rENG}That makes sense.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你什么意思? \N{\rENG}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很久前的战争中 珍珠非常自豪\N{\rENG}Back during the war, Pearl took pride
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}能为你的母亲拿生命冒险\N{\rENG}in risking her destruction for your mother.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她将玫瑰看得比什么都重要--\N{\rENG}She put Rose Quartz over everything--
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}高过理智 无视后果 不惧死亡\N{\rENG}over logic, over consequence, over her own life.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.04,0:07:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还好吗 伙计? \N{\rENG}You okay, dude?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.90,0:07:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得做点什么! \N{\rENG}I have to do something!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你告诉我这些! 再见! \N{\rENG}Thanks for telling me that! Bye!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}记着 康妮\N{\rENG}Remember, Connie.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在激烈战斗中 史蒂文才是最重要的\N{\rENG}In the heat of battle, Steven is what matters.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而你无足轻重\N{\rENG}You don't matter.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我无足轻重\N{\rENG}I don't matter.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在 我们开始吧! \N{\rENG}Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮? \N{\rENG}Connie?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 你在哪? \N{\rENG}Connie, where are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮! \N{\rENG}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不会刚好看到了康妮 是吧? \N{\rENG}You wouldn't have happened to see Connie, would you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}探测到未注册战斗人员\N{\rENG}Unregistered combatant detected.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮! \N{\rENG}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文? 你在这里干嘛? \N{\rENG}Steven? What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 我不想让你在做这些了--不能独自一人\N{\rENG}Connie, I don't want you to do this anymore--not alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 史蒂文 我现在明白了\N{\rENG}No, Steven. I understand now.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的遗产 你的使命--你是一切! \N{\rENG}Your legacy, your destiny--you are everything!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我--我什么都不是\N{\rENG}And I--I am nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.84,0:08:18.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我能为你做这个 我可以为你效劳\N{\rENG}But I can do this for you. I can give you my service.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 我不需要！\N{\rENG}No! I don't want you to.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我这是为了你啊! \N{\rENG}Steven, I'm doing this for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得能够保护你\N{\rENG}I need to be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但如果由你来保护我\N{\rENG}But if you're the one protecting me,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那又有谁保护你呢? \N{\rENG}then who's the one protecting you?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}迟早有一天 我们会遭遇非常强大的敌人\N{\rENG}Someday soon, we may be fighting some really bad guys.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而当那一天来临时 我希望与你战斗 一起\N{\rENG}And when that day comes, I want to fight with you, together.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.74,0:08:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以 求求你 你愿意跟我一起分享果酱吗? \N{\rENG}So, please, won't you share this jam with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真是简单太多了\N{\rENG}This is much easier.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是重点\N{\rENG}That's the idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不论面对什么 我们共同面对! \N{\rENG}No matter what comes, we do this together!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.72,0:09:08.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 不要干涉 她需要独自面对我\N{\rENG}Steven, don't interfere. She needs to take me on herself.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么? 我们是团队\N{\rENG}Why? We're a team.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她是草莓...\N{\rENG}She's the strawberry...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.14,0:09:18.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}...而他是饼干\N{\rENG}...And he's the biscuit!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我们则是\N{\rENG}And that makes us
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.86,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}果酱\Njam{\rENG}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙伴\Nbuds{\rENG}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS\pos(960,800)}蛤? \N{\rENG}Wha...?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}够了! \N{\rENG}Enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! \N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在实际战斗中 史蒂文可不会及时拯救你! \N{\rENG}In a real battle, Steven won't be there to save you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}错 我会的! \N{\rENG}Yes, I will!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你根本不了解\N{\rENG}Steven, you don't know that.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}错 我了解! \N{\rENG}Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果康妮要战斗 我们要一起战斗! \N{\rENG}If Connie is going to fight, we're going to fight together!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错! \N{\rENG}That's right!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不应接近任何战斗! \N{\rENG}You shouldn't be anywhere near the fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你太过重要了! \N{\rENG}You're too important!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并不是! \N{\rENG}I am not!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然 你就是! \N{\rENG}Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! \N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.48,0:10:10.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么不让我为你做这些呢 玫瑰! ? \N{\rENG}Why won't you just let me do this for you, Rose!?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.76,0:10:19.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...我是指...让她 做这些\N{\rENG}I...I mean...Let her do this.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么不让康妮为你做这些? \N{\rENG}Why won't you let Connie do this for you?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今天就到此为止吧\N{\rENG}That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 珍珠...\N{\rENG}Hey, Pearl...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不是故意给你的训练捣乱的\N{\rENG}I didn't mean to mess up your training.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.20,0:10:41.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你那些 "你毫不重要"的言论真的令我害怕\N{\rENG}But all that "you're nothing"talk was really freaking me out.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰让你感觉你毫不重要吗? \N{\rENG}Did Rose make you feel like you were nothing?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.14,0:10:51.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰让我感觉我最为重要\N{\rENG}Rose made me feel like I was everything.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我现在了解了你们相互间多么在意彼此\N{\rENG}I see now how deeply you care about each other.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那会让你们都成为伟大的骑士! \N{\rENG}That will make you both great knights!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮基本上是个专家了\N{\rENG}Connie is practically an expert.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以 史蒂文 你要花很多功夫赶上康妮\N{\rENG}So, Steven, you have a lot of catching up to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我真是太高兴了\N{\rENG}Oh, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我等不及进行空中与水下决斗训练了\N{\rENG}I can't wait for the midair and underwater dueling exercises.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这会非常有趣的! \N{\rENG}It's going to be boodles of fun!
